# hardware: só as 2 peças FINAIS de impressão vão pro repo (protocolo 3MF).
# print/ = frente multicor + capa (só bater o olho e imprimir); sim/ = mockups
# STL p/ conferir encaixe no FreeCAD; LEIA-ME.txt = manual. Fontes .scad, tools,
# refs, peças de teste e legados ficam locais (fora do repo).
hardware/*
!hardware/Case/
hardware/Case/*
!hardware/Case/LEIA-ME.txt
!hardware/Case/print/
hardware/Case/print/*
!hardware/Case/print/frente-multicor.3mf
!hardware/Case/print/case-capa.3mf
!hardware/Case/sim/
hardware/Case/sim/*
!hardware/Case/sim/sim-tela-modulo.stl
!hardware/Case/sim/sim-esp32-capa.stl
